# Innvikta CyberHelp — SEO Audit Review & Fix Report

---

## What the Audit Got RIGHT (and we fixed)

| Audit Issue | Problem | Fix Applied |
|---|---|---|
| Page invisible to Google | [index.html](file:///c:/Users/Tadse/OneDrive/Desktop/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/index.html) only had `<div id="root">` — zero crawlable content | Added `<noscript>` with H1, 5-step guide, crime types, key resources (~300 words) |
| Weak meta title | Generic, no search intent | Updated to: *"Cybercrime Help India \| Report & Recover \| Innvikta CyberHelp"* |
| Weak meta description | Vague, no keywords | Rewritten: action-first, mentions 1930, account freezing, cybercrime.gov.in |
| No schema markup | Zero JSON-LD | Added 4 schema blocks — details below |
| No geo signals | No Pune/Maharashtra/India in static HTML | Added in `LocalBusiness` schema + static fallback |
| No Open Graph / Twitter Card | Missing entirely | Full OG + Twitter Card tags added |
| No keywords meta tag | Missing | 9 targeted keywords added |
| No GEO / AI search targeting | AI tools had nothing to cite | `FAQPage` schema with 5 Q&As targeting Google AI Overviews and ChatGPT/Perplexity |

### JSON-LD Schema Blocks Added

| Schema Type | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `WebSite` | Site identity for Google's Knowledge Graph |
| `LocalBusiness` | Pune, Maharashtra location — enables local SEO |
| `WebPage` | Breadcrumb + mentions of I4C and NCRP (government authority signals) |
| `FAQPage` | 5 real questions targeting high-intent queries for AI/Google answer boxes |

