## What the Audit Got WRONG

> **Root Cause:** The auditor crawled the page before JavaScript loaded, saw only an empty `<div id="root">`, and assumed all content was missing. In reality, your React app had strong UX content already.

| Auditor Claim | Reality |
|---|---|
| *"No emergency 1930 banner"* | [EmergencyBanner.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Tadse/OneDrive/Desktop/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/src/components/EmergencyBanner.jsx) — Golden Hour banner already existed |
| *"Hero tone is corporate"* | [HeroSection.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Tadse/OneDrive/Desktop/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/src/components/HeroSection.jsx) — *"Fraud Happened? Stay Calm. Act Fast."* was already empathetic |
| *"No crime-type cards"* | [SectionCards.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Tadse/OneDrive/Desktop/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/src/components/SectionCards.jsx) — 13 categorized tool cards already present |
| *"No step-by-step guide"* | [FilingGuide](file:///c:/Users/Tadse/OneDrive/Desktop/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/src/components/FilingGuide.jsx#123-223) section already existed |
| *"No 1930 CTA"* | [Navbar.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Tadse/OneDrive/Desktop/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/Cyberhelp_Innvikta%20new/src/components/shared/Navbar.jsx) — **Call 1930** button already in navbar |
| *"No mobile sticky helpline"* | Mobile hamburger menu already opened to a **Call 1930** button |

