## Next Steps to Activate SEO Gains

1. **Upload** updated `dist/` folder to your server
2. **Validate** schema at [search.google.com/test/rich-results](https://search.google.com/test/rich-results)
3. **Submit URL** in Google Search Console → Request Re-indexing
4. Allow **1–2 weeks** for Google to re-crawl and reflect changes
